These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, white, green
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who likes green is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | green | blue     | white | blood-red |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, crime, satire, epic
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Movie-Genre     | western    | satire | crime | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bus, scooter, jet-ski
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Transport   | bus   | scooter   | subway  | jet-ski |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, milk, water
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking cola and the egyptian##2
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | juice | cola | water | milk  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

