.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rowing, climbing, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is sailing##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | volleyball | sailing | climbing | rowing     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

