.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, drama, epic, documentary
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the fan of electronic is the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | drama    | animation | documentary |

