.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, filmmaking, writing
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, snake, goat
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Pet   | snake       | goat       | pony | frog |

