.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, r&b, jazz
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the fan of country is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Music-Genre           | r&b     | jazz | blues    | country     |

