.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep, d&b, house
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | hip-hop | house  | d&b      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

