.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, dancing, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, june, september, january
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Birthday   | january     | february       | june   | september      |

