.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, swimming, surfing, skateboarding
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola    | milk  | fanta |
| Sport   | snowboarding       | swimming | surfing | skateboarding  |

