The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Sport   | biathlon        | swimming       | skateboarding   | soccer |
| Job    | security-guard | entrepreneur | doctor | coach  |

